b'FC Bayern is sending out a new, strong signal for diversity. Like Real Madrid, Juventus, Manchester United and Arsenal, the treble winners are participating in the "Human Race" initiative run by partner adidas, under which designer Pharrell Williams has developed special jersey collections. FC Bayern is taking this action as the start of its own, further-reaching campaign, which is to raise awareness for tolerance and peaceful coexistence by the end of the year.
